flowchart TD
    A([Authenticated user]) --> B{User action}
    B -- Click normal Logout --> C[Revoke current session only]
    C --> D[Other devices remain signed in]
    D --> E([Return to login])

    B -- Change password --> F[Enter current and new password]
    F --> G{Select Log out all devices?}
    G -- No --> H[Update password and refresh current session]
    H --> I([Continue on current device])
    G -- Yes --> J[Revoke every session]
    J --> K[Create fresh session for current device]
    K --> I
